column2: select AssetID=a.ID --AssetNodeDist=an.NodeDist   , TractID=t.ID --TractNodeDist=tn.NodeDist, d.*   , MilesMin=MIN(d.Miles)   , MilesMax=MAX(d.Miles)   , MinutesMin=MIN(d.Minutes)   , MinutesMax=MAX(d.Minutes)   , N=count(*) from optw.tamass.ASSETS a    join optw.ptheta.Portland1#Assets an on a.ID=an.ID    join optw.ptheta.Portland1#Drive d on an.NodeID=d.OrigNodeID or an.NodeID=d.DestNodeID   join optw.ptheta.Portland1#Tracts tn on tn.NodeID=d.OrigNodeID or tn.NodeID=d.DestNodeID   join optw.tamass.TRACTS t on tn.ID=t.ID where an.NodeDist < @nodedistmax and tn.NodeDist < @nodedistmax    and Minutes < # group by AssetID, TractID
